# Working area for the stb_vorbis divergence-detection harness
# (`tools/diff_vorbis/diff_run.sh`). Holds the instrumented
# source copy, the per-compiler driver binaries, and the trace
# diffs. Regenerated on demand; not source of truth.
/.diff_vorbis/
